{"name": "odoo-addon-account-reconcile-oca", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-account-reconcile-oca", "version": "17.0.1.3.5", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 17.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/account-reconcile", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo-addon-account_reconcile_model_oca", "odoo-addon-account_statement_base", "odoo"], "summary": "Reconcile addons for Odoo CE accounting", "upload_time": 1731930272}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Faccount--reconcile-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/account-reconcile\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/account-reconcile/tree/17.0/account_reconcile_oca\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/account-reconcile-17-0/account-reconcile-17-0-account_reconcile_oca\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/account-reconcile&target_branch=17.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-etobella: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/etobella.png?size=40px\n    :alt: etobella\n    :target: https://github.com/etobella\n    ```\n---\n\n# Account Reconcile Oca\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:dcb5036258ed1a909c8df332f82e015b39a2d10c5a2a55d2f19dfe1917062e1d\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis addon allows to reconcile bank statements and account marked as\nreconcile.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n### Bank reconcile\n\nAccess Invoicing / Dashboard with a user with Full Acounting\ncapabilities. Select reconcile on the journal of your choice.\n\n### Account reconcile\n\nAccess Invoicing / Accounting / Actions / Reconcile All the possible\nreconcile options will show and you will be able to reconcile properly.\nYou can access the same widget from accounts and Partners.\n\n## Known issues / Roadmap\n\nThe following bugs are already detected:\n\n- Creation of activities on the chatter do show automatically\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/account-reconcile/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/account-reconcile/issues/new?body=module:%20account_reconcile_oca%0Aversion:%2017.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- CreuBlanca\n- Dixmit\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Enric Tobella\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-etobella }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/account-reconcile](https://github.com/OCA/account-reconcile/tree/17.0/account_reconcile_oca) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_reconcile_oca.models.account_journal", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 Dixmit", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_reconcile_oca.models.account_journal.AccountJournal", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_reconcile_oca.models.account_journal.AccountJournal.get_rainbowman_message", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_reconcile_oca.models.account_journal.AccountJournal._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_reconcile_oca.models.account_journal.AccountJournal.reconcile_mode", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_reconcile_oca.models.account_journal.AccountJournal.company_currency_id", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_reconcile_oca.models.account_journal.AccountJournal.reconcile_aggregate", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_reconcile_oca.models.account_account_reconcile", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 Dixmit", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_reconcile_oca.models.account_account_reconcile.CharId", "bases